
Unix:
  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake ..
  make

WIN:
  - manually set "EIGEN3_INCLUDE_DIRS"
  - After generating the Visual Studio files, highlight the "tspline" project -> Properties -> C/C++ -> All Options and remove the option "--Wunused-function"
  - Visual Studio: Project->Properties->C/C++->Code Generation->Enable C++ Exceptions:Yes
